#: ../../source/concepts.rst:2
msgid "Core Concepts"
msgstr "核心概念"

#: ../../source/concepts.rst:4
msgid "This guide explains the fundamental concepts that power Fabricatio."
msgstr "本指南介绍驱动 Fabricatio 的基本概念。"

#: ../../source/concepts.rst:7
msgid "Event-Driven Architecture"
msgstr "事件驱动架构"

#: ../../source/concepts.rst:9
msgid ""
"Fabricatio uses an event-driven architecture where agents respond to "
"events rather than direct method calls. This pattern enables loose "
"coupling and flexible composition."
msgstr ""
"Fabricatio 采用事件驱动架构，Agent 通过响应事件而非直接调用方法来执行任务。"
"这种模式实现了松耦合和灵活的组合。"

#: ../../source/concepts.rst:12
msgid "Event System"
msgstr "事件系统"

#: ../../source/concepts.rst:14
msgid "Events are the triggers that initiate workflow execution:"
msgstr "事件是触发工作流执行的触发器："

#: ../../source/concepts.rst:26
msgid "Events support:"
msgstr "事件支持："

#: ../../source/concepts.rst:28
msgid "**Quick instantiation**: ``Event.quick_instantiate(name)``"
msgstr "**快速实例化**：``Event.quick_instantiate(name)``"

#: ../../source/concepts.rst:29
msgid "**String conversion**: ``.collapse()`` returns the event name"
msgstr "**字符串转换**：``.collapse()`` 返回事件名称"

#: ../../source/concepts.rst:30
msgid "**Custom payload**: Events can carry data (see advanced usage)"
msgstr "**自定义载荷**：事件可以携带数据（参见高级用法）"

#: ../../source/concepts.rst:33
msgid "EventEmitter Pattern"
msgstr "EventEmitter 模式"

#: ../../source/concepts.rst:35
msgid "The ``EventEmitter`` provides publish-subscribe functionality:"
msgstr "``EventEmitter`` 提供发布-订阅功能："

