#: ../../source/concepts.rst:353
msgid "Best Practices"
msgstr "最佳实践"

#: ../../source/concepts.rst:355
msgid ""
"**Always use async/await** Never mix sync and async code without proper "
"handling."
msgstr ""
"**始终使用 async/await** 切勿在没有适当处理的情况下混合同步和异步代码。"

#: ../../source/concepts.rst:358
msgid "**Handle exceptions** Use try/except for graceful error handling:"
msgstr "**处理异常** 使用 try/except 进行优雅的错误处理："

#: ../../source/concepts.rst:368
msgid ""
"**Set appropriate timeouts** Configure timeouts for long-running "
"operations:"
msgstr ""
"**设置适当的超时** 为长时间运行的操作配置超时："

#: ../../source/concepts.rst:376
msgid ""
"**Use structured output for reliability** Prefer ``aask_structured()`` "
"over ``aask()`` when possible."
msgstr ""
"**使用结构化输出以提高可靠性** 尽可能优先使用 ``aask_structured()`` 而非 ``aask()``。"
